      <title>KMP</title>
      <link href="/2022/08/01/KMP/"/>
      <url>/2022/08/01/KMP/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="KMP"><a href="#KMP" class="headerlink" title="KMP"></a>KMP</h1><h2 id="Border"><a href="#Border" class="headerlink" title="Border"></a>Border</h2><p>约定：字符串 $S$ 的长度为 $n$, $[l,r]$ 的子串是 $S_{l,r}$, 前缀 $S_{1,i} = pre_i$， 后缀 $S_{n - i + 1, n} = suf_i$<br>定义字符串 $S$ 的一个 Border 为一个满足 $pre_i=suf_i$ 的前缀，其中 $S$ 和 $\emptyset$ 也是 $S$ 的 Border<br>记 $S$ 的 Border 集合为 $B(S)$，设最长的 Border 为 $LBorder$</p><h2 id="Period（周期）"><a href="#Period（周期）" class="headerlink" title="Period（周期）"></a>Period（周期）</h2><p>若 $0 &lt; p \le n, S[i] = S[i + p], \forall i \in [1, n]$，则称 $p$ 为 $S$ 的一个 Period<br>记最小 Period 为 $per(S)$<br><em>结论</em>：$p$ 是 $S$ 的 Period $\Leftrightarrow$ $|S|-p$ 是 $S$ 的 Border<br><em>证明</em>：<br>$p$ 是 $S$ 的 Period $\Leftrightarrow S[i-p] = S[i]$<br>$q$ 是 $S$ 的 Border $\Leftrightarrow S[1,q]=S[n-q+1, n] \Leftrightarrow S[1] = S[n-q+1]$<br>令 $i=p+1$ 即可得到 $S[p+1-p]=S[n-q+1]=S[p+1]$ 即<br>$n-q+1=p+1$ 即 $n=p+q$</p><h2 id="Weak-Periodicity-Lemma"><a href="#Weak-Periodicity-Lemma" class="headerlink" title="Weak Periodicity Lemma"></a>Weak Periodicity Lemma</h2><p>若 $p$ 和 $q$ 是 $S$ 的 Period，$p + q \le n$, 则 $gcd(p,q)$ 也是 $S$ 的 Period<br><em>证明</em>:<br>设$p &lt; q$, 记 $d=q-p$<br>若 $i&gt;p$, 则 $i-p&gt;0$, 故 $S[i]=S[i-p]=S[i-p+q]=S[i-d]$<br>若 $i \le p$, 则 $i+q\le n$, 故 $S[i]=S[i+q]=S[i+q-p]=S[i-d]$<br>因此, $d$ 也是 $S$ 的 Period, 更相减损, 故得证</p><h2 id="Periodicity-Lemma"><a href="#Periodicity-Lemma" class="headerlink" title="Periodicity Lemma"></a>Periodicity Lemma</h2><p>若 $p, q$ 是 $S$ 的 Period，且 $p + q \le |S| + gcd(p, q)$ ，则 $gcd(p,q)$ 也是 $|S|$ 的一个Period<br><del>证明看起来非常复杂</del></p><h2 id="LBorder"><a href="#LBorder" class="headerlink" title="LBorder"></a>LBorder</h2><p>对于一个字符串 $p$，$p$ 的 Border 的 Border 也是 $p$ 的 Borde，因此可以通过$p[i - 1]$ 的最长 Border 来推出 $p[i]$ 的最长 Border<br>不妨令 $p[1, j] = p[i - j, i - 1]$ ($p[1,j]$ 为 $p[i - 1]$ 的最长 Border)，$next[j]$ 为 $p[j]$ 的最长 Border长度：</p><ol><li>若 $p[j + 1] = p[i]$， 则：$j = j + 1，next[i] = j$  </li><li>若 $p[j + 1] \ne p[i]$ ，则令 $j$ 跳到 $next[j]$ 再次进行匹配<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">2</span>, j = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt;= n; i ++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(j &amp;&amp; p[i] != p[j + <span class="number">1</span>]) j = next[j];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(p[i] == p[j + <span class="number">1</span>]) j ++;</span><br><span class="line">    next[i] = j;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>这段代码也可以理解为： 让 $p$ 后移一位变为 $p’$，然后让 $p’$ 的前缀去匹配 $p$ 的后缀（自己匹配自己）</li></ol><h2 id="KMP-匹配"><a href="#KMP-匹配" class="headerlink" title="KMP 匹配"></a>KMP 匹配</h2><p>对于文本串 $s$ ，模式串 $p$，若 $s[i - j, i - 1] = p[1, j]$，即模式串的前缀 $j$ 已经匹配成功<br>如果 $s[i] \ne p[j + 1]$，那么只需要令 $j$ 跳到 $next[j]$ 再次进行匹配<br>如果 $s[i] = p[j + 1]$，说明可以匹配则令 $j = j + 1$ ，如果 $j = n$ 说明模式串匹配成功 </p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>, j = <span class="number">0</span> ; i &lt;= m; i ++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(j &amp;&amp; s[i] != p[j + <span class="number">1</span>]) j = next[j];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(s[i] == p[j + <span class="number">1</span>]) j ++;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(j == n)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; i - j + <span class="number">1</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>; </span><br><span class="line">        j = next[j];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="例题"><a href="#例题" class="headerlink" title="例题"></a>例题</h2><p><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P3375">P3375 【模板】KMP字符串匹配 </a></p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> N = <span class="number">1e5</span> + <span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> ne[N], n, m;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    string s, p; cin &gt;&gt; s &gt;&gt; p;</span><br><span class="line">    m = s.<span class="built_in">length</span>(), n = p.<span class="built_in">length</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    s = <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span> + s, p = <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span> + p;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">2</span>, j = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt;= n; i ++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span>(j &amp;&amp; p[i] != p[j + <span class="number">1</span>]) j = ne[j];</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(p[i] == p[j + <span class="number">1</span>]) j ++;</span><br><span class="line">        ne[i] = j;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>, j = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt;= m; i ++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span>(j &amp;&amp; s[i] != p[j + <span class="number">1</span>]) j = ne[j];</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(s[i] == p[j + <span class="number">1</span>]) j ++;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(j == n)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            cout &lt;&lt; i - j + <span class="number">1</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            j = ne[j];</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; i ++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; ne[i] &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&#x27; &#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/1200/E">Problem - 1200E - Codeforces</a><br>将 $n$ 个字符串合并成一个字符串。合并两个字符串 $A$, $B$ 时，删除 $B$ 中与 $A$ 的后缀重合的最长前缀，比如将 “sample” 和 “please” 合并为 “samplease”<br>很容易想到将 $B$ 拼到 $A$ 的前面，这样形成 $BA$ 只需要找到这个字符串的最长 border 长度，合并时删去这个 border 就好了。（注意合并时候为了防止越界在中间加一个特殊字符）</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">kmp</span><span class="params">(string s)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> n = s.<span class="built_in">length</span>();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">2</span>, j = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt;= n; i ++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(j &amp;&amp; s[i] != s[j + <span class="number">1</span>]) j = ne[j];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(s[i] == s[j + <span class="number">1</span>]) j ++;</span><br><span class="line">ne[i] = j;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> ne[n - <span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">solve</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> n; cin &gt;&gt; n;</span><br><span class="line">string ans, x;</span><br><span class="line">cin &gt;&gt; x; ans = x;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt; n; i ++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">cin &gt;&gt; x;</span><br><span class="line">string t = <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span> + x + <span class="string">&quot;^^&quot;</span> + ans;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> tmp = <span class="built_in">kmp</span>(t);</span><br><span class="line">ans = ans + x.<span class="built_in">substr</span>(tmp);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; ans;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后T了， 考虑到每一次合并的 ans 比较长，而且 ans 前面的字符对答案没有贡献<br>比如：$abfdsarsewfvdsarreab$ 和 $aba$ 拼在一起的时候前面只需要保留 ans 的后三位，$abaeab$ 即可</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> len = <span class="built_in">min</span>(ans.<span class="built_in">size</span>(), x.<span class="built_in">size</span>());</span><br><span class="line">string t = x + <span class="string">&quot;^^&quot;</span> + ans.<span class="built_in">substr</span>(l1 - len);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当然这样还是T了<br>又犯了一个犯了很多次的错误 不应该直接这样拼接，换成+=就成功过掉了（再犯这个错误就紫砂）</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">string t = x;</span><br><span class="line">t += <span class="string">&quot;^^&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">t += ans.<span class="built_in">substr</span>(l1 - len);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P4824">USACO15FEB] Censoring S</a><br>在字符串 $s$ 中，重复删除同一个字串 $t$。直到 $t$ 不再是 $s$ 的字串为止，$|s|\le10^6$<br>考虑用一个栈来维护 $s$, 和 $t$ 匹配成功后就将匹配的部分弹出。这样看起来就很对，但是样例没跑过。<br>问题在忽略了删除后两边重新凑成 $t$ 的情况，那么用一个数组记录一下 $s[i]$ 已经匹配到的 $t$ 的位置（类似于next数组），匹配成功后弹出相应的部分，$j$ 跳到栈首位置匹配到 $t$ 的位置就可以啦</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">solve</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">string s, p; cin &gt;&gt; s &gt;&gt; p;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> n = p.<span class="built_in">size</span>(), m = s.<span class="built_in">size</span>();</span><br><span class="line">p = <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span> + p, s = <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span> + s;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; <span class="title">ne</span><span class="params">(n + <span class="number">100</span>)</span>, <span class="title">f</span><span class="params">(m + <span class="number">100</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">2</span>, j = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt;= n; i ++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(j &amp;&amp; p[j + <span class="number">1</span>] != p[i]) j = ne[j];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(p[j + <span class="number">1</span>] == p[i]) j ++;</span><br><span class="line">ne[i] = j;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">stack&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; st;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>, j = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt;= m; i ++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(j &amp;&amp; s[i] != p[j + <span class="number">1</span>]) j = ne[j];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(s[i] == p[j + <span class="number">1</span>]) j ++;</span><br><span class="line">f[i] = j;</span><br><span class="line">st.<span class="built_in">push</span>(i);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(j == n)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> x = <span class="number">0</span>; x &lt; n; x ++) st.<span class="built_in">pop</span>();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(st.<span class="built_in">size</span>()) j = f[st.<span class="built_in">top</span>()];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span> j = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">string ans = <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(st.<span class="built_in">size</span>())&#123;</span><br><span class="line">ans += s[st.<span class="built_in">top</span>()]; st.<span class="built_in">pop</span>();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">reverse</span>(<span class="built_in">all</span>(ans));</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; ans;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
